---

The layout, as described above, with `align-items: center` disabled on the primary flex container (`.container`), allows items `.b` &amp; `.c` to wrap because the `::before` pseudo item occupies all space in a previous column with `flex-basis: 100%`. The viewport sets the height limitation and break point for the wrap.

